 él. Federico se asusta cuando Moncho y otro peón quieren sacarlo de la habitación donde se encuentra a la fuerza." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3094000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentRatingKey="67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg" grandparentTitle="La Trepadora" grandparentType="show" index="51" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" title="S01:E051" userState="0"><Image alt="S01:E051" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E051" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E051" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1776518234" duration="3094000" endsAt="1776521328" id="69da3fcc069ffd78c3b586da" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776548037" duration="3093000" endsAt="1776551130" id="69da3fcc069ffd78c3b586e4" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video guid="plex://episode/69da3fca069ffd78c3b586c7" key="/library/metadata/69da3fca069ffd78c3b586c7" ratingKey="69da3fca069ffd78c3b586c7" summary="Carlos Raúl y César han llegado a casa de los Palacios. A punto de llorar, el gordo toma a la pequeńa entre sus brazos." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="2965000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1672730.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/69b0b83aba3a6d319e0e710b" grandparentKe